{{Top|leg|title=''Censian''-class transport}}
The '''''Censian''-class transport''' was a ship class used to move cargo and passengers. It could host at least 400 passengers.<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports">[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]</ref>

The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] used ''Censian''-class transports to transport [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends|SpecForces Marines]]. One of their ships was the ''[[Hauler VI]]''<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports" />

